Vim config for terminal and GUI.

FIRST TIME SETUP
------------------------------------------------------------------
Add the following symlinks
   ~/.vimrc -> vim-config/vimrc
   ~/.gvimrc -> vim-config/vimrc
   ~/.vim -> vim-config
   ~/.gvim -> vim-config
Fetch Vundle.vim
   $ cd vim-config/bundle
   $ git clone https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim.git Vundle.vim
Start vim and enter following command
   :PluginInstall
